
NOTE

on each description section, item , must contain : date-publication, order, last_modified, title

fields related to date, must start with 'date', and are the only ones!
ex : date, date-publication, date-debut-promotion, date-evenement, ...
	with form.value : current_date_int, empty_date_int ,and regional : current_date_fr, empty_date_fr, ..
	



mecanisme COMMENT : 

1 : comment_add_text_from_input
- in current, when create file/ section, add a form input as comment to ref
- must be tag input !
2 : comment_add_text_from_section
- in a section metadata, when create/display, define a comment common to all items on this section
3 : input_reference_comment
- auto, add comment about input value when created to ref
4: comment_add_text_on_create


